						               													<description>BonDing is a science-themed card game set in the world of ChemCaper. Players aim to 'bond' as many Petticles as possible with their cards before the game ends. There are different kinds of bonds, elements and Petticles in the game that can be found and bonded together.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A number of petticles will be available for the player to attempt and bond.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To bond Petticles, players must collect the required Orb cards through taking turns exchanging and drawing Orb cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Then, the player can 'bond' them into Petticles that are on the table by playing those cards and naming the type of bond of the Petticle: Metallic, Covalent or Ionic.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are two modes of play, Classic and Competitive. Both use easy-to-understand rules that vary.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It is an educational game that can be played without any prior chemistry knowledge.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
